    Throw Errors.NotImplemented with "Transition matrix estimation not yet implemented"

Process called "higher_order_markov_chain" that takes state_sequence as List[String], order as Integer returns MarkovChain:
    Note: Construct higher-order Markov chain with memory length > 1
